  <div class="text-8xl font-bold w-full dark:text-[#f0f0f0] flex justify-center items-center">Google Developers Group</div>
  <div class="w-3/4 text-xl dark:text-white flex flex-col gap-5 mx-auto">
    <div class="w-4/3">Join a Google Developer Group to build new skills and connect with local developers, online and in person.</div>


    <div class=" w-4/3">Whether you're a beginner or a pro, all interested in technology are welcome in this inclusive community.</div>
  </div>
  </div>
  </div>
